  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101450/extras/9873645d0a06c76ceee456dc67cb9b97.avif?t=1748405968\" width=616 height=346 /></span><strong><br><br>In <i>Paws & Potions</i>, </strong>play as a kitten in third-person view, racing against time to help Emília the witch prepare potions before nightfall! <br><br>Deliver the correct ingredients as quickly as possible and discover the world around you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101450/extras/7e1fd571158153754d7d8233fcc3e4bf.avif?t=1748405968\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAMILY BUSINESS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the cat of Emília  and Laura it's your job to help them run their business, ensuring quick and clean service. Whether aided by Edgar — a wise old book — or working alone, bring the correct and properly processed ingredients to the cauldron and watch the magic happen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of the day, you can rest in your cozy little bed... Or take advantage of your free time to explore the garden!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101450/extras/bd1690585fa26a646fce55ace6656bbd.avif?t=1748405968\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEYOND THE GARDEN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and discover new areas and ingredients as you complete tasks. Navigate through swamps, forests, and ruins in search of lost treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and uncover secrets in each of the new areas: new shortcuts, new mechanics, and maybe even... new problems?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101450/extras/1a42a2fe7b72dd1dfe30ae8fb84e2085.avif?t=1748405968\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101450/extras/9873645d0a06c76ceee456dc67cb9b97.avif?t=1748405968\" width=616 height=346 /></span><strong><br><br>In <i>Paws & Potions</i>, </strong>play as a kitten in third-person view, racing against time to help Emília the witch prepare potions before nightfall! <br><br>Deliver the correct ingredients as quickly as possible and discover the world around you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101450/extras/7e1fd571158153754d7d8233fcc3e4bf.avif?t=1748405968\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FAMILY BUSINESS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the cat of Emília  and Laura it's your job to help them run their business, ensuring quick and clean service. Whether aided by Edgar — a wise old book — or working alone, bring the correct and properly processed ingredients to the cauldron and watch the magic happen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the end of the day, you can rest in your cozy little bed... Or take advantage of your free time to explore the garden!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101450/extras/bd1690585fa26a646fce55ace6656bbd.avif?t=1748405968\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BEYOND THE GARDEN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock and discover new areas and ingredients as you complete tasks. Navigate through swamps, forests, and ruins in search of lost treasures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and uncover secrets in each of the new areas: new shortcuts, new mechanics, and maybe even... new problems?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3101450/extras/1a42a2fe7b72dd1dfe30ae8fb84e2085.avif?t=1748405968\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p>",
